===Etymology===
From [[gamete]] + [[-phyte]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#{{botany}} The [[plant]] (or the [[haploid]] [[phase]] in its [[life cycle]]) which produces [[gamete]]s by [[mitosis]] in order to produce a [[zygote]].

